                        <interp inst="t18370814-1884-verdict-1" type="verdictSubcategory" value="no_subcategory"></interp>GUILTY</rs>
                  </hi>. Aged 26.—
<rs id="t18370814-1884-punishment-107" type="punishmentDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18370814-1884-punishment-107" type="punishmentCategory" value="transport"></interp>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-1884-18370814 t18370814-1884-punishment-107"></join>Transported for Life</rs>.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Before Mr. Justice Williams.</hi>
